places.address: 7F9R+759 Zama Masjid, Kanker, NH 43, Kanker, Chhattisgarh 494334

featured_reviews.review_id:
Since zama masjid has a unique monumental architecture which gives a landmark to the town and a place of remembering god.
Front of this masjid is a bus stop , stationery shop and market area.

Front of the masjid is also The chaupati  caupaattii of Kanker town where one can get the tasty veg/non veg street food . This is at heart of Kanker town and one the happening place..

Ultimately excellent place to visit ..
